# Experiment runs are NOT versioned: their artifacts embed AMBROSIA-derived
# content (questions, gold queries, executed outputs), and AMBROSIA's authors ask
# that it not be redistributed. Regenerate them locally — see experiments/README.md.
experiments/*
!experiments/README.md
!experiments/NOTICE.md
